{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286413, "create_time": 1657447612, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "#48246", "timestamp": 1657447612}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286414, "create_time": 1657447674, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "河南银行和理财并没有本质区别，你买理财可也是再正规不过的银行了，难道理财亏了就要国家赔？", "timestamp": 1657447674}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286418, "create_time": 1657447713, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: #48246", "timestamp": 1657447713}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286419, "create_time": 1657447772, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Alice: 不用跟这洞主掰扯，大概它姓赵", "timestamp": 1657447772}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286420, "create_time": 1657447828, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 就这个帖子也并没有说政府该赔，一个没有定性的事情，就直接冲政府？政府还在帮你抓人", "timestamp": 1657447828}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286424, "create_time": 1657448046, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 但是他反驳了你说的所有论点", "timestamp": 1657448046}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286425, "create_time": 1657448052, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 那你政府敢定性说这不是存款吗，这都几个月了。", "timestamp": 1657448052}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 286426, "create_time": 1657448059, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3